  <brief_title>RCT to Investigate Whether an Exercise Programme Improves the Physical Performance and QOL After BMT</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomised Controlled Trial to Investigate the Effects of an Exercise Programme on Physical Performance and Quality of Life After a Bone Marrow Transplant</official_title>
